OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775909467
OL,3,CTwo arrested following murder in
OL,4,CPrimrose Hill
OL,6,FDetectives investigating the murder of
OL,7,F21-year-old Finbar Sullivan have
OL,8,Farrested two men following the fatal
OL,9,Fstabbing in Primrose Hill on Tuesday,
OL,10,F7 April.
OL,12,FOfficers arrested a 27-year-old man on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of murder on Friday, 10
OL,14,FApril. He was arrested alongside a 25-
OL,15,Fyear-old man on suspicion of assisting
OL,16,Fan offender.
OL,18,FThe pair remain in police custody.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
