OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775909467
OL,3,CTwo arrested following murder in
OL,4,CPrimrose Hill
OL,6,F"Although we have made two arrests, my
OL,7,Fofficers continue to work around the
OL,8,Fclock to trace everyone involved. I'd
OL,9,Flike to thank the public who have come
OL,10,Fforward with information so far. If
OL,11,Fyou are yet to speak to us, or share
OL,12,Ffootage from Tuesday relating to this
OL,13,Fincident, please do not hesitate to
OL,14,Fget in touch. Anything you submit
OL,15,Fcould have a huge impact on our
OL,16,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
