OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775909467
OL,3,CTwo arrested following murder in
OL,4,CPrimrose Hill
OL,6,F"In the meantime, residents can expect
OL,7,Fto see an increased police presence as
OL,8,Fdedicated local officers continue
OL,9,Fpatrols in Primrose Hill and the
OL,10,Fsurrounding areas."
OL,12,FThose with relevant information can
OL,13,Fupload it to the police major incident
OL,14,Fportal here, or contact police on 101,
OL,15,Fquoting reference 6448/07Apr. An
OL,16,Fanonymous report can be made via
OL,17,FCrimestoppers on 0800 555 111.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@SO]
